do n't torture a duckling ( italian : non si sevizia un paperino ) is a 1972 italian giallo film directed by lucio fulci , starring florinda bolkan , tomas milian and barbara bouchet . it is significant within fulci 's filmography as it is one of the first in which he began using violent gore effects , something he would continue to do in his later films , most notably zombi 2 , the beyond and city of the living dead . the soundtrack was composed by riz ortolani and features vocals by ornella vanoni .